{"data":{"wpPage":{"uri":"/media-buying/","nodeType":"Page","seo":{"title":"Media Buying Agency | The PM Group Advertising","metaDesc":"The PM Group is San Antonio's largest media buying agency. We provide digital media buying, radio, television, print and outdoor planning & buying.","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","opengraphTitle":"Media Buying Agency | The PM Group Advertising","opengraphDescription":"The PM Group is San Antonio's largest media buying agency. We provide digital media buying, radio, television, print and outdoor planning & buying.","opengraphImage":null,"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/media-buying/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"articleType":[],"pageType":["WebPage"],"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"/media-buying/#webpage\",\"url\":\"/media-buying/\",\"name\":\"Media Buying Agency | The PM Group Advertising\",\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"/#website\"},\"datePublished\":\"2021-05-25T12:48:04+00:00\",\"dateModified\":\"2021-07-16T20:15:56+00:00\",\"description\":\"The PM Group is San Antonio's largest media buying agency. We provide digital media buying, radio, television, print and outdoor planning & buying.\",\"breadcrumb\":{\"@id\":\"/media-buying/#breadcrumb\"},\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"ReadAction\",\"target\":[\"/media-buying/\"]}]},{\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"@id\":\"/media-buying/#breadcrumb\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Media Buying\"}]}]}"}},"mediaBuyingFields":{"mediaBuyingHero":{"title":"Media Buying","backgroundImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/a4412/expertise-hero.png","srcSet":"/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/0b5bc/expertise-hero.png 480w,\n/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/53a05/expertise-hero.png 960w,\n/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/a4412/expertise-hero.png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/7ad73/expertise-hero.webp 480w,\n/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/ca5fc/expertise-hero.webp 960w,\n/static/ee86ab39295e9cf0a7f96aa08412e716/57ff5/expertise-hero.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"}]},"width":1920,"height":400}}}}},"textImageSection":{"textAboutDescription":"<p>With all the <a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/our-work/\">media choices</a> available to advertisers, it can be hard to choose the right one. For starters, many clients/advertisers quite honestly don’t have the ability to garner the lowest prices. The primary goal of media buying is getting maximum exposure to the most people at the lowest cost possible.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>That is where The PM Group media buying professionals come in. We purchase more media in the San Antonio market than any ten agencies combined! That media power assures The PM Group clients they get the best rates available. Even our smallest clients enjoy the same rates as our multi-million-dollar clients receive. That’s unmatched buying power!</p>\n","textAboutTitle":"NO ONE BUYS MORE MEDIA IN SOUTH TEXAS THAN THE PM GROUP, SAN ANTONIO'S LARGEST ADVERTISING AND MARKETING AGENCY.","textAboutImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/cd301/iStock-1247049968-scaled.png","srcSet":"/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/b0667/iStock-1247049968-scaled.png 640w,\n/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/7f1f2/iStock-1247049968-scaled.png 1280w,\n/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/cd301/iStock-1247049968-scaled.png 2560w","sizes":"(min-width: 2560px) 2560px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/f2d34/iStock-1247049968-scaled.webp 640w,\n/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/cf392/iStock-1247049968-scaled.webp 1280w,\n/static/0a0923e57c669bdc601dc961dae6d462/98808/iStock-1247049968-scaled.webp 2560w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 2560px) 2560px, 100vw"}]},"width":2560,"height":1707}}}}},"mediaBuyingGrid":{"gridContent":[{"mbTitle":"What is media buying?","mbContent":"<p>Media buying is the process of purchasing media placements for advertising on radio, broadcast TV, cable advertising, billboards, magazines, digital advertising, or other print publications. It’s a common service among advertising and marketing agencies. The primary goal of media buying is getting maximum exposure to as many people at the lowest cost possible. This is the major point of difference with The PM Group’s media department. Everyone wants our prices!</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/abe50/What-is-Media-Buying.png","srcSet":"/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/2b3ff/What-is-Media-Buying.png 50w,\n/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/e06f2/What-is-Media-Buying.png 100w,\n/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/abe50/What-is-Media-Buying.png 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/b8a94/What-is-Media-Buying.webp 50w,\n/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/2367f/What-is-Media-Buying.webp 100w,\n/static/cfdf8471c583071080de78376a973959/11d28/What-is-Media-Buying.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"}]},"width":200,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Why is professional media buying necessary?","mbContent":"<p><strong>Media buying expertise.</strong> The PM Group’s media buyers are always on top of the latest trends in the industry. They have also been around long enough to know what works and what doesn’t work best. With your business goals in mind, we are, therefore, able to provide you with the best path to follow to grow your business. The other benefit is our leverage and buying networks, which The PM Group has established over the last 30 years, giving us trust and buying power.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/b9457/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.png","srcSet":"/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/1f9d3/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.png 49w,\n/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/f910d/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.png 98w,\n/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/b9457/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.png 195w","sizes":"(min-width: 195px) 195px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/9164d/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.webp 49w,\n/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/4a9d7/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.webp 98w,\n/static/b36f3bdd0b9a78ca302c3d087b4bc62d/f4ddd/Why-is-Proff-Media-Buying-Necessary.webp 195w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 195px) 195px, 100vw"}]},"width":195,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Who is a media buyer?","mbContent":"<p>For a better flow in the media buying process, let’s define who a media buyer is.</p>\n<p>This is the individual responsible for the negotiation and placement of your ads on television, radio, digital, and print or any other advertising medium.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/ef7bc/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.png","srcSet":"/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/1f9d3/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.png 49w,\n/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/c4ce0/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.png 97w,\n/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/ef7bc/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.png 194w","sizes":"(min-width: 194px) 194px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/9164d/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.webp 49w,\n/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/700ec/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.webp 97w,\n/static/6527f79bf1d72b7f25d6a9b69a211e7d/f82e8/Who-is-A-Media-Buyer.webp 194w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 194px) 194px, 100vw"}]},"width":194,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"How does digital media buying work?","mbContent":"<p>Digital media buying simply means the process of acquiring display and video ad placements on apps, websites, and other digital platforms.</p>\n<p>From geo-fencing to retargeting, from paid serial to programmatic buying, Connected TV and more, The PM Group can deliver best in class placements at the lowest cost available with full reporting capabilities to ensure your marketing dollars have performed as planned.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/a70f4/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.png","srcSet":"/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/abbb8/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.png 67w,\n/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/fb7e8/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.png 134w,\n/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/a70f4/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.png 268w","sizes":"(min-width: 268px) 268px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/84ce2/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.webp 67w,\n/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/f98f1/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.webp 134w,\n/static/11345ecc17f140d7ad97a6b68b611e4f/2966a/How-Does-Digital-Media-Buying-Work-1.webp 268w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 268px) 268px, 100vw"}]},"width":268,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"The process of media planning and buying","mbContent":"<p>The three phases of media buying at The PM Group include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pre-launch:</strong> Strategizing on vital media decisions</li>\n<li><strong>Launch:</strong> Ensuring media delivery is effective and runs as per the plan</li>\n<li><strong>Post-launch:</strong> Auditing and measuring campaign results, and making any necessary adjustments for maximum benefits</li>\n</ul>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/2ad1c/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.png","srcSet":"/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/abbb8/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.png 67w,\n/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/a92b4/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.png 134w,\n/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/2ad1c/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.png 267w","sizes":"(min-width: 267px) 267px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/84ce2/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.webp 67w,\n/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/057be/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.webp 134w,\n/static/67047c47e8d30fdb348641481236c948/c3fd6/The-Process-of-Media-Planning-and-Buying.webp 267w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 267px) 267px, 100vw"}]},"width":267,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Key steps to media planning","mbContent":"<p>Media planning is essential in any marketing decision. This helps identify all the resources required and evaluate available options in an effort to maximize any client’s investment and results.</p>\n<p>This reduces the risk of failure of any media campaign.</p>\n<p>When The PM Group does media buying, we find it is always best to take time to lay out all the aspects that will go into the campaign to avoid any client disappointments. That is a primary reason our clients stay with us for decades versus just a couple of years. The PM Group focuses on client results, NOT the pursuit of new clients to replace the ones we anticipate losing. How crazy is that? Happy, satisfied clients don’t leave a successful relationship with their advertising agency.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/d62cd/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.png","srcSet":"/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/fab85/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.png 79w,\n/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/632af/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.png 158w,\n/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/d62cd/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.png 315w","sizes":"(min-width: 315px) 315px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/86849/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.webp 79w,\n/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/5a25b/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.webp 158w,\n/static/cb4cea5771c80461bca752866e7e9116/cfb7f/Key-Steps-To-Media-Buying.webp 315w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 315px) 315px, 100vw"}]},"width":315,"height":198}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Know your target market","mbContent":"<p>Advertising is only useful when it reaches the right audience. Poor research on who your primary target audience should be will lead to poor media planning &amp; poor media buying and, subsequently, poor results.</p>\n<p>Here are the key questions we want all of The PM Group’s clients to the able answer when choosing their target audience:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who do you want your message to reach?</li>\n<li>Who is your primary target?</li>\n<li>What is their gender?</li>\n<li>How old are they?</li>\n<li>How much income do they earn?</li>\n<li>Where do they specifically reside?</li>\n<li>Where do they work–what is their profession?</li>\n<li>Are they married, engaged, single?</li>\n<li>Does the desired target have certain education attainment levels?</li>\n</ul>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/abe50/Know-Your-Target-Market.png","srcSet":"/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/2b3ff/Know-Your-Target-Market.png 50w,\n/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/e06f2/Know-Your-Target-Market.png 100w,\n/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/abe50/Know-Your-Target-Market.png 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/b8a94/Know-Your-Target-Market.webp 50w,\n/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/2367f/Know-Your-Target-Market.webp 100w,\n/static/0afe29ed81bbbc47e015faeedd910fd7/11d28/Know-Your-Target-Market.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 200px) 200px, 100vw"}]},"width":200,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Understand your target audience","mbContent":"<p>Once you identify the consumer group you are targeting, we like to master their behavioral traits. This will help us in determining where to place your ad dollars most effectively. If you do not have adequate funds in our professional opinion to launch an effective campaign, we will tell you so. If your budget is inadequate, we won’t spend client money if it is destined to fail. That’s the level of experience and integrity The PM Group brings to the table for our clients.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/a89cc/Understand-Your-Target-Market.png","srcSet":"/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/f8b59/Understand-Your-Target-Market.png 37w,\n/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/93fcd/Understand-Your-Target-Market.png 73w,\n/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/a89cc/Understand-Your-Target-Market.png 146w","sizes":"(min-width: 146px) 146px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/aaa00/Understand-Your-Target-Market.webp 37w,\n/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/a6e6f/Understand-Your-Target-Market.webp 73w,\n/static/7591f77bc3e0df07cbd43d3e5cf55cbe/48e56/Understand-Your-Target-Market.webp 146w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 146px) 146px, 100vw"}]},"width":146,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"What is your competitor up to?","mbContent":"<p>Our media buying professionals perform research to know exactly what successful methods your competitor is using. The following insight about your competition can help you answer this question comprehensively:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Who is your primary competition targeting?</li>\n<li>What media sources are they buying?</li>\n<li>In what programs are they running their campaigns?</li>\n<li>What dayparts are they placing their ads?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These answers will help us create media buys that will allow your business to compete favorably in the market.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/8721f/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.png","srcSet":"/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/bb550/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.png 60w,\n/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/ea4a0/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.png 121w,\n/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/8721f/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.png 241w","sizes":"(min-width: 241px) 241px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/c5f0b/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.webp 60w,\n/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/71aeb/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.webp 121w,\n/static/cae0df77a491431d8d3d386121b27b30/3e705/What-is-Your-Competitor-up-to.webp 241w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 241px) 241px, 100vw"}]},"width":241,"height":200}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Create your media strategy","mbContent":"<p>Based on your industry knowledge on who your primary target audience is, where we can find them, and having a defined understanding of your key competitors’ marketing moves–The PM Group media team can come up with a winning strategy for our clients. It’s what we have done successfully for over 30 years and we are still the marketing and advertising leader in our space.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/8f38f/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.png","srcSet":"/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/1bd09/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.png 48w,\n/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/478e5/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.png 96w,\n/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/8f38f/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.png 191w","sizes":"(min-width: 191px) 191px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/d0131/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.webp 48w,\n/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/089f6/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.webp 96w,\n/static/2635d43df206edc6f2060a70ff8d011a/3f510/Create-Your-Media-Strategy.webp 191w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 191px) 191px, 100vw"}]},"width":191,"height":191}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Analyzing campaign performance","mbContent":"<p>This is an area that our marketing and advertising agency competitors cannot measure up to our stringent media buying standards. We are the only San Antonio area advertising agency that guarantees their clients two specific key differences: <strong>the combination of the lowest prices and a 100% or greater audience delivery</strong>.</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/849f2/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.png","srcSet":"/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/2b3ff/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.png 50w,\n/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/7316e/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.png 99w,\n/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/849f2/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.png 198w","sizes":"(min-width: 198px) 198px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/b8a94/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.webp 50w,\n/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/e209a/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.webp 99w,\n/static/13585bda0418ae5d724ccc4faa369195/42fe9/Analyzing-Campaign-Performance.webp 198w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 198px) 198px, 100vw"}]},"width":198,"height":198}}}}},{"mbTitle":"Ask yourself this question:","mbContent":"<p>If you went to the supermarket and bought 4 bags of groceries and they only put 3 bags in your car, wouldn’t you demand you receive the missing groceries? That is what happens when a media buying agency does not 100% guarantee their media performance for their clients!</p>\n","mbImage":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/15129/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.png","srcSet":"/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/28ae8/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.png 63w,\n/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/52c35/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.png 126w,\n/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/15129/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.png 252w","sizes":"(min-width: 252px) 252px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/de5cd/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.webp 63w,\n/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/d6fca/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.webp 126w,\n/static/8db6f93b700ef383a14b0e11546081e4/1238c/Ask-Hourself-This-Question.webp 252w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 252px) 252px, 100vw"}]},"width":252,"height":191}}}}}]}}}},"pageContext":{"breadcrumb":{"location":"/media-buying/","crumbs":[{"pathname":"/","crumbLabel":"Home"},{"pathname":"/media-buying","crumbLabel":"media-buying"}]}}}